Privacy Policy for BMI Calculator

Effective Date: 04-11-2024

At BMI Calculator, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our app.

1. Information We Collect
We do not collect any personal information from users when they use our app. The only information processed by the app is the height (cm) and weight (kg) that you voluntarily input for the purpose of calculating your Body Mass Index (BMI).

2. How We Use Your Information
The information you provide is used solely for the following purposes:

To calculate your BMI based on the height and weight you enter.
To provide you with instant feedback on your BMI category.
3. Data Storage
The data you enter (height and weight) is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to any servers or third-party services. We do not retain any of your data after you close the app.

4. Third-Party Services
We do not use any third-party services or APIs that collect, store, or analyze your personal data. Our app is designed to operate independently without sharing user information with any external parties.

5. Children's Privacy
Our app is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so we can take appropriate action.

6. Security
We take the security of your data seriously. However, please remember that no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the app. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: mdjakariaibnaazamkhan@gmail.com
By using the BMI Calculator app, you consent to this Privacy Policy.
